<FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="Segoe UI"><FONT SIZE=5 STYLE="font-size: 17pt"><SPAN STYLE="font-weight: normal">离退休人员遗属抚恤费发放办法
</SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT>
</H2>
<P CLASS="cjk" ALIGN=CENTER STYLE="page-break-inside: avoid; widows: 4; orphans: 1; page-break-after: auto">
<IMG SRC="" ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=32 BORDER=0><IMG SRC="" ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=32 BORDER=0></P>
<P CLASS="cjk" ALIGN=CENTER STYLE="page-break-inside: avoid; widows: 4; orphans: 1; page-break-after: auto">
<FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="宋体"><FONT SIZE=4><SPAN LANG="zh-CN">一、根据湘人发</SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT><FONT FACE="Calibri, serif"><SPAN LANG="en-US"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="微软雅黑, serif"><FONT SIZE=4><SPAN LANG="en-US">[2009]94</SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="宋体"><FONT SIZE=4><SPAN LANG="zh-CN">号文件，所属遗属抚恤发放对象的人员可以申请办理遗属抚恤费。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS="cjk" ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="page-break-inside: avoid; widows: 129; orphans: 1; page-break-after: auto">
<FONT COLOR="#000000">&nbsp;<FONT FACE="宋体"><FONT SIZE=4><SPAN LANG="zh-CN">二、无工作人员持当地派出所证明，完全丧失劳动能力的持相关证明到退休科办理遗属抚恤金。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS="cjk" ALIGN=CENTER STYLE="page-break-inside: avoid; widows: 4; orphans: 1; page-break-after: auto">
<FONT COLOR="#000000">&nbsp;<FONT FACE="宋体"><FONT SIZE=4><SPAN LANG="zh-CN">三、遗属抚恤对象每年</SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT><FONT FACE="Calibri, serif"><SPAN LANG="en-US"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="微软雅黑, serif"><FONT SIZE=4><SPAN LANG="en-US">5</SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="宋体"><FONT SIZE=4><SPAN LANG="zh-CN">月、</SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT><FONT FACE="Calibri, serif"><SPAN LANG="en-US"><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="微软雅黑, serif"><FONT SIZE=4><SPAN LANG="en-US">11</SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000"><FONT FACE="宋体"><FONT SIZE=4><SPAN LANG="zh-CN">月带本人身份证到退休办审核。未经审核人员不得发放遗属抚恤费。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT></P>
<P CLASS="cjk" ALIGN=CENTER STYLE="page-break-inside: avoid; widows: 4; orphans: 1; page-break-after: auto">
